Class Vaccine

java.lang.Object
Vaccine
public class Vaccine extends Object
This java program defines a class Vaccine with different attributes corresponding to the information regarding the Vaccine.
Author:
mukeshangrish The Vaccine class also has multiple accessors and mutators in order to provide flexibility during object creation and modification. There are also methods to convert object to string and to compare different Vaccine objects
